   Peng, Li-Ning; Lee, Wei-Ju; Chen, Liang-Kung, Taipei Vet Gen Hosp, Ctr Geriatr \& Gerontol, 201,Sect 2,Shih Pai Rd, Taipei 11217, Taiwan.
   Hsiao, Fei-Yuan; Huang, Shih-Tsung, Natl Taiwan Univ, Coll Med, Grad Inst Clin Pharm, Taipei, Taiwan.
