   Jin, Jiashun, Carnegie Mellon Univ, Dept Stat, Pittsburgh, PA 15213 USA.
   Lin, Huazhen, Southwestern Univ Finance \& Econ, Sch Stat, Ctr Stat Res, Chengdu 611130, Sichuan, Peoples R China.},
