   Lei, Yalan; Tang, Rong; Xu, Jin; Zhang, Bo; Liu, Jiang; Liang, Chen; Meng, Qingcai; Hua, Jie; Yu, Xianjun; Wang, Wei; Shi, Si, Fudan Univ, Pancreat Canc Inst, Shanghai, Peoples R China.},
