   Suri, Jasjit S., Global Biomed Technol Inc, Knowledge Engn Ctr, Roseville, CA 95661 USA.
   Jena, Biswajit, SOA Deemed Univ, Inst Tech Educ \& Res, Dept Comp Sci \& Engn, Bhubaneswar, India.},
