   Ziegler, Andreas, StatSol, Lubeck, Germany.
   Wright, Marvin N., Leibniz Inst Prevent Res \& Epidemiol BIPS, Bremen, Germany.},
Keywords-Plus = {REGRESSION},
Author-Email = {fouodo@imbs.uni-luebeck.de
   inke.koenig@imbs.uni-luebeck.de
