   Li, Wenhua; Wang, Qianwen; Lu, Junxia; Zhao, Bin; Geng, Yuqing; Wu, Xiangwei; Chen, Xueling, Natl Hlth \& Hlth Commiss, Key Lab Prevent \& Treatment High Morbid Cent Asia, Shihezi, Peoples R China.
