   Cha, Jae Myung, Gang Dong KyungHee Univ Hosp, Dept Gastroenterol, Seoul, South Korea.
   Won, Geun Hui, Catholic Univ Daegu, Sch Med, Dept Psychiat, Daegu, South Korea.
   Cho, Yong Hyuk, Ajou Univ, Grad Sch, Dept Med Sci, Suwon, South Korea.},
