   Lin, Siying; Yang, Yuedong, Sun Yat Sen Univ, Sch Comp Sci \& Engn, Guangzhou 510006, Peoples R China.
   Wang, Shitian, Sun Yat Sen Univ, Sch Life Sci, Guangzhou 510275, Peoples R China.},
