   Grimm, Christina; Komnidi, Anastasia; Hussong, Michelle; Schweiger, Michal R., Univ Cologne, Fac Med, Ctr Mol Med Cologne CMMC, Cologne, Germany.
   Herling, Carmen Diana; Kreuzer, Karl-Anton; Hallek, Michael, Univ Cologne, Fac Med, Dept Internal Med 1, Cologne, Germany.
   Herling, Carmen Diana; Kreuzer, Karl-Anton; Hallek, Michael, Univ Cologne, Fac Med, German CLL Study Grp, Cologne, Germany.
   Herling, Carmen Diana; Kreuzer, Karl-Anton; Hallek, Michael, Univ Cologne, Fac Med, Ctr Integrated Oncol CIO Aachen Bonn Cologne Dues, Cologne, Germany.
