   Luo, Feng; Yuan, Xue-mei; Wang, Qiu-yi; Chen, Chang-ming; Yao, Xue-ming; Ma, Wu-kai, Guizhou Univ Tradit Chinese Med, Affiliated Hosp 2, Dept Rheumatol \& Immunol, 83 Feishan St, Guiyang 550001, Guizhou, Peoples R China.
