   Liu, Dengyao, Xinjiang Med Univ, Xinjiang Key Lab Translat Biomed Engn Res, Dept Intervent Radiol, Tumor Hosp,Clin Med Coll 3, Urumqi, Peoples R China.
   Zhu, Zhihua, Sun Yat Sen Univ, Guangdong Prov Clin Res Ctr Canc, Collaborat Innovat Ctr Canc Med,Dept Thorac Surg, State Key Lab Oncol South China,Canc Ctr, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.},
