   Williams, Craig; Merkle, Shannon, Informat Management Serv Inc, Rockville, MD USA.
   He, Chuan, Univ Chicago, Inst Biophys Dynam, Dept Biochem \& Mol Biol, Chicago, IL USA.
   He, Chuan, Univ Chicago, Howard Hughes Med Inst, Chicago, IL USA.},
