   Wu, Ziqi; Gong, Liya; Luo, Jingwen; Wen, Junyan; Hao, Yanyu; Wen, Ge, Southern Med Univ, Nanfang Hosp, Dept Med Imaging, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Xiaobo, Southern Med Univ, Guangdong Prov Peoples Hosp, Guangdong Acad Med Sci, Dept Radiol, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Xiaobo, Guangdong Prov Key Lab Artificial Intelligence Med, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.
