   Mervin, Lewis, AstraZeneca, Mol AI, Discovery Sci, R\&D, Cambridge CB2 0AA, England.
   Engkvist, Ola, Chalmers Univ Technol, Dept Comp Sci \& Engn, S-41296 Gothenburg, Sweden.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.ailsci.2025.100128},
EarlyAccessDate = {FEB 2025},
