   Wu, Chunlan; Liu, Jie; Wan, Luying; Wang, Rixiong, Fujian Med Univ, Affiliated Hosp 1, Natl Reg Med Ctr, Dept Oncol, Binhai Campus, Fuzhou 350212, Peoples R China.
