   Zhang, Tian-yi; Yan, Hao; Wang, Jieying; Zhou, Hang; Lu, Renhua; Fang, Wei; Wang, Qin; Che, Xiajing; Huang, Jiaying; Jin, Haijiao; Shen, Jianxiao; Zhou, Yin; Mou, Shan; Fang, Yan, Shanghai Jiao Tong Univ, Ren Ji Hosp, Sch Med, Dept Nephrol, Shanghai, Peoples R China.
