   Zheng, Xiaoxuan, Shanghai Jiao Tong Univ, Shanghai Chest Hosp, Dept Resp Endoscopy, Dept Resp \& Crit Care Med,Sch Med, 241 Huaihai West Rd, Shanghai 200030, Peoples R China.},
