   El-Shafai, Walid, Menoufia Univ, Fac Elect Engn, Dept Elect \& Elect Commun Engn, Menoufia, Egypt.
   Khan, Jawad, Gachon Univ, Sch Comp, Seongnam, South Korea.},
DOI = {10.32604/cmes.2026.076798},
Article-Number = {41},
Keywords = {Colorectal cancer; immunotherapy; microsatellite instability; tumor
