   Ma, Han, Peoples Hosp Liaoning Prov, Dept Radiol, Shenyang, Peoples R China.
   Zhu, Hehe; Liu, Bitian, Shengjing Hosp China Med Univ, Dept Urol, Shenyang, Peoples R China.},
