   Haddadin, Sara, Univ Jordan, Amman, Jordan.
   Alshwayyat, Mustafa, Jordan Univ Sci \& Technol, Fac Med, Irbid, Jordan.
   Talafha, Muna, Univ Mississippi, Med Ctr, Dept Pathol, Jackson, MS USA.
   Hanifa, Hamdah, Univ Kalamoon, Fac Med, Al Nabk, Syria.
   Muhaidat, Jihan, Jordan Univ Sci \& Technol, Fac Med, Dept Dermatol, Irbid, Jordan.
