   Gong, Aifeng, Nanjing Med Univ, Dept Gen Practice, Huaian Peoples Hosp 1, Huaian 223300, Jiangsu, Peoples R China.
   Yin, Yunfan, Gen Hosp Western Theater Command, Dept Otolaryngol Head \& Neck Surg, Chengdu 610083, Sichuan, Peoples R China.
   Zhang, Jialing, Nanjing Med Univ, Dept Gastroenterol, Huaian Peoples Hosp 1, Huaian 223300, Jiangsu, Peoples R China.},
