   Liang, Bing; Li, Juan, Shanghai Geriatr Med Ctr, Dept Orthopaed Surg, Shanghai 201104, Peoples R China.
   Liang, Bing; Hu, Annan; Zhou, Jian; Dong, Jian, Fudan Univ, Zhongshan Hosp, Dept Orthopaed Surg, Shanghai 200032, Peoples R China.
